        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1507578436" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3485596401585373749">I cannot help but visualize Belle Boyd as Erica Kane in crinolines. Her chapters inevitably had me laughing my head off.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


